name: Periodic Table on Cardano
description: PeriodicTable.io is a complete, accurate and visually stimulating “Periodic Table of Elements” all living on the Cardano blockchain. With this project we bring together science and art. We're taking a useful tool, The Periodic Table of Elements, and making it visually cool while still retaining its scientific properties. All this while making it a community owned project on the Cardano blockchain.
